layoutDesc.layout:
Ll. 1-2 cut on the whole width; from l. 3 on in two columns, each entry ending with a numeral, preceded by a space after the personal name;
                                    there is also, whenever possible, a small space between own name and father's name; fragment b belongs to the lower part of column i; fragment c belongs to the lower part of 
                                    column ii.

